PN,39602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1780416668
OL,3,C'The pitch was immaculate': Everton
OL,4,Cgroundsman retires after 38 years
OL,6,F"It's been an absolute joy working
OL,7,Fwith people here. It's been more like
OL,8,Fa hobby than a job."
OL,10,FJoining the club from Liverpool City
OL,11,FCouncil in 1988, Bob went on to work
OL,12,Funder 14 permanent managers.
OL,14,FHe remembers the elite demands of
OL,15,FColin Harvey and Howard Kendall, as
OL,16,Fwell as clashing with Walter Smith,
OL,17,Fwho once threatened to sack him for
OL,18,Fmowing the pitch in a circular pattern
OL,19,Fbecause it resembled rival Celtic's
OL,20,Fground.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
