PN,39603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1780416668
OL,3,C'The pitch was immaculate': Everton
OL,4,Cgroundsman retires after 38 years
OL,6,FDuring his long tenure, Bob proudly
OL,7,Flost only a handful of matches to the
OL,8,Funpredictable British weather,
OL,9,Fensuring the turf remained "world-
OL,10,Fclass" for both the men's and women's
OL,11,Fteams.
OL,13,FIn retirement, Bob plans to tend to
OL,14,Fhis own garden in Maghull, enjoy
OL,15,Fcoarse fishing, and spend time with
OL,16,Fhis grandchildren. He will also
OL,17,Ffinally get to experience match days
OL,18,Fas a supporter.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/4
